In the INTEREST OF K.E., Minor Child, K.E., Minor Child, Appellant. No. 18-0796 Court of Appeals of Iowa. Filed May 1, 2019

DECISION WITHOUT PUBLISHED OPINION

See Iowa R. App. P. 6.904

A minor appeals after being adjudicated a delinquent for theft in the second degree, possession of stolen property. AFFIRMED.

AFFIRMED.
